# Bidding API Test

### Get bid info for a product (requires login)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bids/info/1
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

### Place a bid (requires login)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bids/place
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: connect.sid=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE

{
  "productId": 1,
  "bidAmount": 150000
}

### Get bid history for a product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bids/history/1

